{"tid":1420581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武術速成班！","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:33:40.000Z","uid":57346,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7a154cde1e7d833a932e6b505ba87779fd755e","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"武術其實係冇速成既，不過可講下有咩可以放棄，你冇練過就係冇練過，冇得勉強！你放棄晒盡量多既動作，留返冇得cut既動作，先免強可以速成。<br />\n<br />\n1.放棄格擋<br />\n<br />\n除非你有盾！果d雙手護頭真係多9餘，你不如逃走啦！最有效既制敵方法係攬低佢！<br />\n<br />\n如果人地冇刀、你又人多過佢，可以用下面兩招！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExY2hrg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExY2hrg.png&h=1a511e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樹熊咁撲上去，之後逃走！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/121040_72dfdd552d17c05aabd79378290207a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F121040_72dfdd552d17c05aabd79378290207a2.png&h=8cf08fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依招係撲落去，之後逃走！<br />\n<br />\n2.放棄重心<br />\n<br />\n本來保持平衡係武術既重中之中，但你冇練過就係冇練過，你知唔知要出一拳有威力又平衡到同時收拳又準又快要練幾耐！<br />\n<br />\n冇錯！我係話收拳又準又快，唔係出拳！講出拳準已經低一階了！<br />\n<br />\n反正做唔到平衡，不如你用全身既力飛出去！對方係你兩步既距離，你就衝四步！<br />\n<br />\n當然前題係人地冇刀、你又人多過佢！<br />\n<br />\n3.放棄逃跑（轉身跑）<br />\n<br />\n我假設人地有刀或鎚仔，一d可以一野ok你既野，而你多人過佢！記住唔好背住佢跑，你要顧自己顧埋身邊既兄弟。唯一安全既地方係敵人背面，你要保持三大步既距離，繞去對方背面，有機會既話飛腳踢低佢。<br />\n<br />\n4.放棄收拳<br />\n<br />\n我睇咁多日既片，發現好多兄弟出拳距離好短，可能因為佢地雙手要顧埋防守，仲有一樣好奇怪既係佢地成日用拳底去揼人，打人應該用拳骨架。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊先係最好既防守，你諗住每次連中四拳自然有最低標準既收拳動作，你由一個稍微遠既起跳點自然有一個最低標準既威力。<br />\n<br />\n係！用跳啦，要理解步法太難喇！用跳代替行啦，反正對手真係超弱！（純粹睇咁多日既片，班黑社會自己都渾身破綻！）<br />\n<br />\n5.放棄進攻<br />\n<br />\n如果人地有刀，或者人多過你，真係冇得打架！<br />\n<br />\n你要用最闊既步幅、最高既提腿高度、最快既腳步轉身跑。拉遠距離去掟雜物，幫其他兄弟走！<br />\n<br />\n掟野都有方法，我上次見住班兄弟係咁TK，咁不如唔好掟！試下用拋啦，唔好諗住拋咁高，打水漂咁平飛出去算喇！<br />\n<br />\n6.放棄恐懼<br />\n<br />\n對方如果係木棍甚至係徒手，你真係唔洗驚，一招KO唔到你，你係危急情況會忘記痛楚，最貼身既距離先可以防止中第二下，當然之後仲要靠其他兄弟幫手。<br />\n<br />\n我再諗下有咩可以改善！大家再討論下。仲好真係要走呀！唔好等d狗黎！"},{"pid":"838c7cff86436c0d81d8d286303735031f329f79","tid":1420581,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/228347/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%81%87%E7%8B%BC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%BA%96-%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB-%E4%BD%86%E9%A1%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%2F228347%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E9%2581%2587%25E7%258B%25BC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25BA%2596-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E9%25A1%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%258A&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e6b6f599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/228347/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%81%87%E7%8B%BC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%BA%96-%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB-%E4%BD%86%E9%A1%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A</a>"},{"pid":"77344110ce701577e8c33d8849ccfeed9c8bb5f7","tid":1420581,"uid":176392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"第3點同第5點係咪有少少矛盾，人地有刀，轉唔轉身跑"},{"pid":"77a6f6b223dcfddd0f190e74e3fe6913c87f960d","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"838c7cff86436c0d81d8d286303735031f329f79","tid":1420581,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/228347/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%81%87%E7%8B%BC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%BA%96-%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB-%E4%BD%86%E9%A1%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%2F228347%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E9%2581%2587%25E7%258B%25BC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25BA%2596-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E9%25A1%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%258A&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e6b6f599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/228347/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E8%A1%93-%E9%81%87%E7%8B%BC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%BA%96-%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB-%E4%BD%86%E9%A1%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"亂噏！做唔到架！<br />\n<br />\n頭幾招打弱點邊有咁易，咁易場場拳賽打半分鐘就完啦。唔好諗住防守反擊呀！<br />\n<br />\n最尾果招關節技起碼要有對等力量，否則點拉直人隻手。<br />\n<br />\n上面堆招式，如果我係女人都冇信心做到！<br />\n<br />\n要甩開人地隻手，只要大風車咁用晒成隻手臂就得甩開人手腕就可以。<br />\n<br />\n唔好天馬行空，唔好睇咁多葉問！"},{"pid":"f9e2c54c743c03d0169e10d627267c18fffb6e94","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77344110ce701577e8c33d8849ccfeed9c8bb5f7","tid":1420581,"uid":176392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"第3點同第5點係咪有少少矛盾，人地有刀，轉唔轉身跑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"如果人地得一兩個就唔洗驚佢"},{"pid":"8eda3728f6fddd4edd6d3c8eac0d06aba1ba3ec0","tid":1420581,"uid":61179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"支持二師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4cedf2ae9952f9560357de5dce9e1bcd6a1aa7","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"7.用武器<br />\n<br />\n其實武器既作用係延長你既攻擊距離，唔係攞黎擋同埋身肉搏架！<br />\n<br />\n首先你要學識用全身既力去下劈，其次要一直保持一個你最遠既攻擊距離。<br />\n<br />\n點用全身既力？好難掌握架！都係果句用跳啦！<br />\n<br />\n攻擊距離係幾遠？由你前腳腳尖開始計兩米米，前腳踏半步、後腳跳半步、武器手臂長度，加埋就有最少兩米。<br />\n<br />\n仲有握法係雙手一前一後虎口位由上而下握住。<br />\n<br />\n成個組合點打？彈入彈出喪劈！速成係咁架喇，但成班人齊心一致，氣勢都嚇死人！"},{"pid":"63a2105a0fa6091b9819073d3db78ca13ed10717","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xHCBh-czvI4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxHCBh-czvI4&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=4dfb983d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xHCBh-czvI4</a>"},{"pid":"baa5f74bef71eaae37d6d986f42e7b38fe545638","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0NfFMy0fCy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0NfFMy0fCy0&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=3fd0747a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0NfFMy0fCy0</a><br />\n<br />\n拐有一樣好處係易上手，你可以當自己揸住兩碌木棍亂咁揮，有拳擊底既可以純粹當護臂同拳套咁用。玩熟左不外乎撥、拍、撞。比起未學過去舞刀弄槍，拐對自己既風險最低。"},{"pid":"f6fb12a682544c945d597355b995cbc7fa50bf5f","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"我用十蚊整左一對<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMA067K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMA067K.png&h=e37459a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木掃把棍一支$9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCLsM7N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCLsM7N.png&h=9772d406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鋸成兩長兩短（5吋x2同18吋x2）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dde5yNO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdde5yNO.png&h=766556fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用電鑽係長段既五吋左右鑽穿佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1J2A09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1J2A09.png&h=0824c108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係短段鑽兩吋深<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJCiTNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJCiTNQ.png&h=6ab81d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三吋螺絲兩支$1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyTYTNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyTYTNR.png&h=68dce896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成品（我發現有少少鬆，下次係駁位落d AA膠先。）"},{"pid":"740868e543eedc59396aaba54bc0cbe69fa8c5c7","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpY6ioZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpY6ioZ.png&h=a14cc69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想象圖"},{"pid":"6fae29c173db30349cf4d44f9143c3e02dc0ad4f","tid":1420581,"uid":61179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6fb12a682544c945d597355b995cbc7fa50bf5f","tid":1420581,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"我用十蚊整左一對<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMA067K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMA067K.png&h=e37459a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木掃把棍一支$9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCLsM7N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCLsM7N.png&h=9772d406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鋸成兩長兩短（5吋x2同18吋x2）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dde5yNO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdde5yNO.png&h=766556fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用電鑽係長段既五吋左右鑽穿佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1J2A09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1J2A09.png&h=0824c108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係短段鑽兩吋深<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJCiTNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJCiTNQ.png&h=6ab81d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三吋螺絲兩支$1<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyTYTNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyTYTNR.png&h=68dce896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成品（我發現有少少鬆，下次係駁位落d AA膠先。）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"帶出街會比黑警當武器喎"}]}